T1  - Ownership and the Changing Employment Relationship: Why Stylized Notions of Labor No Longer Generally Apply—A Reply to Zardkoohi and Paetzold
AU  - Rousseau, Denise M.
AU  - Shperling, Zipi
Y1  - 2004/10/01
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2004.14497608
